  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To collect and organize data into a repository for future research.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To collect and organize data into a repository from the Principal Investigator's (H. Francis
      Farhadi, MD, PhD) patients who are undergoing spinal arthrodesis and/or spinal arthroplasty
      procedures at Ohio State University for future research, as yet to be identified. This
      comprehensive database of patients will allow for gathering of relevant information for
      potential future research use.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
